  "description": {
    "zh": "我们有另一个任务需要你完成，仔细听好了。\n我们通缉名单上的某人最近成功逃离了塔科夫，但他通过雇佣走私者将特定货物运送到外界进行交易。\n\n根据消息，这笔订单需要一套俄军装备，包括头盔、防弹衣和 AK 步枪。计划是将这些物品放置在交易商同意的地点，然后我们的人会追踪它们。你需要找到坠毁在 森林 中间的 24 号飞机残骸，进入驾驶舱并将这些物品藏在那里。注意其他PMC的动向。\n我们期待你的好消息。",
    "en": "We have another task for you, listen carefully.\nSomeone who has been on our wanted-list for a while now managed to get out of Tarkov, however he has been dealing with certain goods by hiring smugglers to get them out of Tarkov into the outside world.\n\nWe were told about an order of a russian army gear set, helmet, vest and AK rifle. The plan is to plant these items in the location the dealers agreed on, then a few of our people will track them down again. You need to locate the plane wreck that has crashed somewhere in the middle of the forest, get inside the cockpit and hide the goods there, and beware of other mercs.\nWe will hear from you soon."
  },
